staging: wilc1000: rename variables prefix using datatype 'u8'

Rename variables with datatype 'u8' in their name to follow the linux
coding style.

Renamed following variables:
u8abort_running_scan
pu8Buffer
pu8keybuf
pu8msa
u8remain_on_chan_flag

